object.customQuery:
select
user_customer_number,
user_name,
rank() over (partition by user_customer_number, policynumber order by created_date desc) as email_number,
PolicyNumber
from 
(select distinct user_customer_number, user_name, created_date 
from dbo.insured_portal_users_stg
where user_active in ('1', '2')
and user_role = 'Insured') ins
join 
(select distinct policynumber, customernumber
from dbo.PolicyDetail) pol
on pol.CustomerNumber = ins.user_customer_number

order by user_customer_number
